    <li><strong>Simple Progress Photo Comparisons</strong>. For physique competitions, photos are key for tracking progress towards your goals.  Our interface provides easy uploading, and photos can be tagged by pose for easy sequential comparisons.</li>
    <li><strong>Historical data tracking</strong>.  All data points are tracked in real time as they are entered and are easy to visualize with graphs and tables.</li>
  </ul>
